README for PacMail
==================

PacMail is an email notifier daemon for Arch Linux (pacman) updates.

DEPENDENCIES
============

python >= 2.5
pacman >= 3.0

INSTALLATION
============

See the 'INSTALL' file.

CONFIGURATION
=============

The PacMail configuration file is located at `/etc/pacmail.conf'.
PacMail may use any SMTP server to send notifications. For local
servers, the values 'smtp_host' and 'sender' must refer to the
server's fully-qualified domain name, e.g. `mail.example.com' and
`user@mail.example.com'.
